        <item>
            <title>2.5.4</title>
            <pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 16:06:37 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>57</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.5.4</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Changes
- Automated `claude -p` / SDK sessions (background memory observers, sub-agents, and other non-interactive runs) are no longer listed in the sidebar Recents or the launcher's session history, keeping the session list focused on your real interactive sessions.
]]></description>
