        <item>
            <title>1.5.0</title>
            <pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 13:13:10 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>13</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.5.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Features
- Add model, effort level, and permission mode selectors to the launcher view
  - Choose between Opus, Sonnet, Sonnet (1M), and Haiku models before starting a session
  - Set effort level (Low, Medium, High, Max) per session
  - Select permission mode (Default, Plan, Auto, Accept Edits, Don't Ask, Bypass All) directly from the launcher
  - All selections persist across app restarts
- Permission mode setting moved from Preferences to launcher for easier per-session control
]]></description>
